---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---
<section
  class="min-h-[90svh] w-full grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center px-6 md:px-12
         bg-[radial-gradient(1600px_600px_at_85%_-10%,rgba(59,130,246,0.2),transparent_60%),radial-gradient(1200px_500px_at_-10%_110%,rgba(236,72,153,0.15),transparent_60%),linear-gradient(180deg,#0a1a2b,#0e2340)]">
  <div class="py-10">
    <h1 class="font-verdana font-extrabold text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-tight mt-3 text-white">
      Impulsa tu crecimiento con estrategia, datos y creatividad
    </h1>

    <p class="text-gray-300 mt-5 max-w-prose text-3xl">
      SEO técnico, performance, contenido y analítica en un solo equipo. Reportes claros y enfoque en ROI.
    </p>

    <div class="flex gap-3 mt-6 flex-wrap">
      <a class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 
          shadow-[0_10px_24px_rgba(234,179,8,.4)]
          bg-linear-to-b from-yellow-400 to-yellow-600 hover:brightness-110 hover:shadow-[0_12px_28px_rgba(234,179,8,.5)]
          transition-all duration-200" href="#contacto">
  Hablar con un experto
</a>
      <a class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold 
          border border-white/30 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white" href="#casosexito">
  Ver casos de éxito
</a>
    </div>

    <p class="text-gray-400 text-2xl mt-4">
      Sin contratos largos · Entregables medibles · Comunicación directa
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="relative min-h-[400px] lg:min-h-[550px] w-full flex justify-center items-center overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] shadow-[0_40px_120px_rgba(0,0,0,.45)]">
  <!-- Video principal -->
  <video 
    src="/videos/Slider-CYC.mp4"
    autoplay 
    muted 
    loop 
    playsinline
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
  ></video>

  <!-- Overlay con degradado azul marino -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0b1a33]/80 via-[#0b1a33]/40 to-transparent"></div>

  <!-- Brillo o reflejo sutil -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/5 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
</div>
</section>